http://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/Remo-granted-conditional-anticipatory-bail-in-minor-verbal-abuse-case/article13986336.ece

The Goa Children's Court on Thursday granted conditional anticipatory bail to singer Remo Fernandes in child verbal abuse case.The court granted him anticipatory bail with condition to produce one surety of Rs.50000/- and directed him to report at Agassaim police station in north Goa for ten days from 10 am to 1 pm and asked him to surrender his passport.Mr. Fernandes is facing a >police FIR for alleged verbal abuse of a minor girl, a victim of car accident.